Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Work Log
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.36,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so, Denroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.42,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.42,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 21\NRebirth of "Die"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.90,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:03.71,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. One can only \Nbecome a man through marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:06.25,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have to do it right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.42,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking from a financial viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's definitely a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:14.19,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Love saves the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.79,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a \Nwedding ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.37,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to combine our efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and help Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.32,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.83,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly so, Enishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.49,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,"Enishing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.74,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,"Enishing" means anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:30.09,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We have no secrets from each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:32.97,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We say anything to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:37.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey, I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.47,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,And what are we congratulating now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.93,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on telling \Nyou formally, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.32,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Please, will you acknowledge \Nour forthcoming marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:49.58,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.54,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:02:59.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.97,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:08.26,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me, do you, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.89,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,But, mark my words, \NI will definitely regain your trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:17.00,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to work at \Nthis inn for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.73,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop calling me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.38,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Within the grounds of Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm to be called "Madam Manager,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,and not Enishi's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.96,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:39.09,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,If you're getting married, make \Nsure you hold a wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.07,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.89,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding ceremonies aren't \Nthere for self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.66,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You have a reputation to uphold as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the successor of Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.39,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got a long way to go \Nbefore you can take charge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.26,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's leftover fish soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.84,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to join us, Miss Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:03.33,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of a reefy coast \Nstings my troubled heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:11.28,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Man... I wasn't expecting her \Nto be so stubborn about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.90,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, she's just telling \Nyou to hold a proper ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:17.11,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's not like she's against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.43,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Holding a wedding reception \Nat an ordinary hotel would
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cost at least 1,600,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't know it would cost that much to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.49,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use Kissuiso for \Nyour grand marriage ceremony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:41.88,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If we help out, \Nmost of the costs would be covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.47,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.22,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.53,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:52.89,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.36,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be interfering with \Nthe inn's normal operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.33,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Like you've never done that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.90,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.74,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, you're in charge of\N the food for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.22,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.69,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to take on extra \Nwaitress duties that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.03,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana and Nako can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.08,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:19.06,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of the food \Nfor the reception?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.34,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Minko, \Nlet's take a look at the market!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:22.71,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:30.18,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I love you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:53.16,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,The days I just circled are \Nsupposed to be the luckiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.67,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there's not even a month left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.58,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Bonbori Festival takes \Nplace in the fall, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.59,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,As the successor, I can't hold my wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the inn is at its busiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Then couldn't you delay \Nthe wedding until after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.55,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What if Takako changes her mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.97,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Enishing, about the cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.31,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:24.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How about some northern pink \Nshrimp and righteye flounders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be food for a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.27,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to keep the costs down, \Nbut I need to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look festive as well as taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so no one will blame me \Nif the food is a little too extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.67,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the dish I had at the \Ncultural festival was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.11,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,That omelet rice with \N"LOVE" written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I could do something \Nsimilar with the carp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:52.02,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Line them up and write \N"LOVE" with miso and vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.10,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.24,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Nori, can I take a look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.15,Default,Nori,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Getting married is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.31,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at an age where I'm supposed \Nto start thinking about that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.07,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,A-Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.53,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I like kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.61,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like at least five or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.66,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,F-Five?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:20.52,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer families to be noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.15,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.17,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.17,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Want to stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:47.90,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.49,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now! \NTake a deep breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:05.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel refreshed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.51,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting a little \Nodd recently, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.45,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, both Mr. Ren \Nand I have been in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the same position as \Nyou, a commis-chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.59,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You may come to a standstill \Nor get irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because things don't work out \Nthe way you want them to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.78,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,but what you gain from hard \Nwork will never betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.02,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets in a slump.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.70,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not what's been bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:40.89,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.67,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.69,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.40,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to make the young \Nmaster's wedding ceremony a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.36,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work with you \Nto make it a success,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.42,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's something I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.19,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,"Make it a success"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.27,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking like Ohana now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.90,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,That girl always manages to \Nget others involved in things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.65,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Before you notice it, \Nyou're a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:18.41,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere at the inn has \Nchanged a lot since she arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.87,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Takako used to be just a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.25,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's make it a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.50,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't copy her too much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.58,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need two troublemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.84,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What else do we need for a wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.52,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some form \Nof entertainment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.08,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.23,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,That means naught \Nwhen up against love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.72,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Money means nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you make remarks like that \Nafter you've finished paying your rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.95,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.54,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.41,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that we could \Nperform a skit at the ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.59,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,like re-enacting how they fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.86,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But can any of us act?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.20,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:12.67,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the perfect line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:21.40,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to get pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've bought so much already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.95,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd practice making it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Can I taste it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.68,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.06,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.46,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I touched something disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.46,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.22,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we keep the cost \Nof the dress this low,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.85,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,we still have the rings \Nto worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.11,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Enishing, I should get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.94,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll see you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.00,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.27,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we can use a rental dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.98,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,The ring can also be cheap-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.23,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:18.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,At least the ring's got to be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.77,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.57,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.18,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.18,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's Nako, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.34,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.02,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Adieu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something bad again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:12:00.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it because I suggested \Nwe hold the wedding here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too much effort for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a wonderful thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and though it may be a lot of work-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.04,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean \Nby "a lot of work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.40,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who \Nsaid we should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.41,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's have the wedding here."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:16.54,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,With your loud, annoying, \Nand disgusting voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:20.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on a sec. \NI'm used to "loud" and "annoying,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,but "disgusting"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:25.43,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who get troubled \Nby your whimsical actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.42,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.34,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:37.84,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're always relying \Non Tohru for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.99,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Repay the debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:48.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.37,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:02.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why Tohru and me-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.03,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're always pretending that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always take the best parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Think about Tohru's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.31,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Take responsibility for \Nchanging Kissuiso's atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.12,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what \Nthe heck you're-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:20.98,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely lost here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I were to go out with Tohru,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Why on Earth are you \Nsaying such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.63,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:48.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like "die" is back in fashion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.09,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's charred!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.19,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.60,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.73,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:03.28,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... there goes breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.16,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.94,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Minko, don't worry about helping \Nout with the wedding anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.69,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.43,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,How can you expect to be trusted \Nif you can't even perform your daily tasks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.36,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in Mr. Ren's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.25,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've \Ngot something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.59,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.04,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ever be able to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.71,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Minko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:34.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-How about we have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:53.62,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's invite Oshimizu and we \Ncan all have lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.91,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some of my fried egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.67,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Oshimizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.05,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher said he \Nwas putting up new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.65,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,But they still look new!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're changing them to red ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:19.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,According to color therapy, it's \Nsupposed to be better for the students' minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.06,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,A red classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.95,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of erotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kind of a \Nwaste, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.62,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.99,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this out of the \Nway and have lunch, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.87,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.80,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.37,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Madam Manager and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.42,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Madam Manager's at a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.88,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,The young master is with Takako,\Nplanning their wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.09,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Planning their wedding, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.07,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Takako's looking out into the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't really seem to \Nbe so gung-ho about the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.59,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she has a lot to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.27,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What was it... marriage browns?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.47,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "Bryans."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:06.36,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, we're helping out with their marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.24,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the person we're \Nhelping out acting this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Your natto's starting to bubble up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.43,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:17.73,Default,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Natto tastes better if you \Nstir it until it gets bubbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.09,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.83,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.88,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I should search somewhere \Nnearer for someone to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.66,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I went off the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.52,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a lot of curtains, \Nso don't worry if you mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.79,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Still, making a wedding \Ndress out of curtains, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.80,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's an incredible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:54.26,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be of some \Nhelp to Takako's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.29,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd lend us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:03.25,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it. \NI love events like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.25,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Ohana going to use the sewing machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:13.88,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,She's apparently not \Nvery good with technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.45,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.53,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What about cellphones?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:21.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I asked Minchi, \Nbut she refused to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:25.14,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tohru likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm not exactly good at noticing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like that situation with Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, but Ko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.30,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow, she's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.75,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,And so accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.38,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you make it cheaper? \NI was your brother's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.98,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:54.31,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 15 years, \Nbut I still remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:55.79,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, don't hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.49,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.24,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm from Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bought a large quantity of\Nfutons from your store six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:14.11,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to call off the \Nwedding with Enishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:28.55,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you \Nwon't acknowledge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:34.05,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I also understand why you can't \Nleave us in charge of this inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:38.42,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I... wanted to have a relationship \Nwith you where we could
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,say anything to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.22,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.04,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,This is something I was \Ngiven by my late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:12.44,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He and I worked at the same inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:16.60,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He was a chef, and I was a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.98,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time we \Ndecided to get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.56,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,the owner gave us an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.60,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He asked whether we'd like to succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an inn that had no successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:36.32,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, we worked hard \Nin order to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:41.07,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Denroku, who worked at the \Nprevious inn, helped us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:50.66,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,We had no time or money to \Nhold a wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.47,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,but he gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In hopes of Kissuiso \Nbecoming successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.93,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,"Kissuiso"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what our inn will be called.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:11.59,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:15.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The kanji in the name means, \N"an inn to please {\i1}you{\i0}," Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.90,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But we should think about \Nthe customers, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:26.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We can't please our customers without \Npleasing ourselves first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:27.68,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:33.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you're pleased, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.19,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:57.06,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He was always by my side after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:02.57,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,He'd always wish for my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.89,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,It's still the same even \Nafter he passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.74,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,"Marriage"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a promise not to let your \Nspouse be alone, ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.23,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,Your spouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:23.12,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, even if one of \Nyou passes away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.97,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:34.64,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, I entrust Enishi's \Nhappiness to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:43.45,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,I... thought I was always \Nbeing opposed by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.32,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,When you told us to have \Nthe marriage ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed you weren't planning \Non letting us succeed the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.16,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.48,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:21:59.77,Default,Takako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:42.72,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for the baiser amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.03,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:45.91,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:46.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.08,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,"Touched"? Oh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 22\NA Determined One-Sided Crush
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:49.33,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
